{"tid":885324,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"鯽魚涌的午餐日記 -7","createTime":"2018-11-01T08:50:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-01T09:03:23.000Z","uid":28951,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cb1fc9d702f3278edc277f26fd9a728691c7d4da","tid":885324,"uid":28951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T08:50:41.000Z","msg":"原本其實唔係打算食呢間，點知行錯路。<br />\n<br />\n經過嘅時候見到入面個設計幾特別，再望望個價錢都唔算貴。<br />\n<br />\n所以試咗呢間先。<br />\n<br />\n鋪面唔算大，二十個位左右。<br />\n<br />\n可能位置比較偏，人少，唔洗等位。<br />\n<br />\n餐牌都係一般cafe嘅嘢。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n落單：番茄焗豬扒飯，餐湯（ 菠菜忌廉 ），特濃朱古力。<br />\n<br />\n湯就落單冇耐已經上抬，隔左5分鐘左右就上埋朱古力。<br />\n<br />\n睇得出啲餐具都有用過心思。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9CCKvwG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9CCKvwG.png&h=d3bd91cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n朱古力都係粉沖，冇乜特別。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t0oaq43.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft0oaq43.png&h=7611fcd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n焗扒飯到。<br />\n<br />\n望落個觀感都唔差但頂頭個啲配菜有點多餘。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SKvHhb4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSKvHhb4.png&h=3fd31017&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n值得一讚嘅係塊豬扒係預先切好嘅。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qTgjjqw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqTgjjqw.png&h=ff49238f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁食嘅時候我地就唔洗再用刀叉咁麻煩，同時佢地焗嘅時候都可以慳返啲時間。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n塊扒唔算大塊，不過時間控制得唔錯，肉唔嚡。<br />\n<br />\n味道偏鹹，番茄味除咗個汁之外都冇乜。<br />\n<br />\n食落先發覺原來有塊䒦士，但完全食唔出。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總結： 普普通通 ，唔加其他飲品都係60蚊左右。<br />\n質素唔係特別差。冇乜人，又唔趕客，hea下吹水都唔錯。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"223049ec00909a31c945c6c35cb89be89949b79d","tid":885324,"uid":83048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T08:52:12.000Z","msg":"幾錢？"},{"pid":"158a561da2793346a79ca0b24ee8a0ffacd5fd62","tid":885324,"uid":114814,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"223049ec00909a31c945c6c35cb89be89949b79d","tid":885324,"uid":83048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T08:52:12.000Z","msg":"幾錢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T09:03:23.000Z","msg":"巴打打少啲丁"}]}